Package com.rb.nonbiz.collections

Interface IidMapVisitors.TwoIidMapsVisitor<VL,​VR>

Enclosing class:
IidMapVisitors
public static interface IidMapVisitors.TwoIidMapsVisitor<VL,​VR>
Useful when you are iterating over 2 maps, and want to cleanly separate out the behavior when an item appears only on the left, only on the right, or on both maps. You could always just do this with a bunch of ifs, but this is cleaner and more functional-looking.
